ties of ~10^9 /cm^3, or with an\nionised `skin' or atmosphere of the molecular torus with densities of ~10^3 -\n10^5 /cm^3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 May 2006 12:53:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
